content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Half made batta

A half made batta is created by preparing a half baked batta by adding ingredients to it. Cooking this will create an unfinished batta, except in the case of a toad batta, where the finished toad batta will be created. It is used in the Gnome Restaurant minigame to make different types of battas for delivery.

  • Half made batta (fruit)
  • Half made batta (toad)
  • Half made batta (worm)
  • Half made batta (vegetable)
  • Half made batta (cheese+tom)
